<law type="statute"><section id="id152"><amendatorysection chaptername="Assignment for Creditors" statutenumber="6-124"><bookinfo>Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2026</bookinfo><statuteno>6-124</statuteno><catchline>Uniformity of application and construction.</catchline><para>In applying and construing the Uniform Assignment for Benefit of Creditors Act, a court shall consider the promotion of uniformity of the law among states that enact it.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 2026, LB783, &#167; 24. </para><effectivedate>July 18, 2026</effectivedate></source></law>
